scripts.gitset-fork: git remote set-url origin git@github.com:AlexseyProhin/dev.git && git remote -v
scripts.build-ext: next build --debug && next export && mv out/_next out/next && sed -i 's/\/_next/\.\/next/g' out/**.html && mv out/index.html extension && rsync -va --delete-after out/next/ extension/next/ && rm -rf out && rsync -va --delete-after public/next-assets extension/
